@startuml
title Use Case D - Candidate Rank Flow
skinparam shadowing false

start
:BusinessSystem\ncall POST rank\n(candidates + optional strategy);
note right
  **No** Index / Vector / Feature\nadapter calls — pure scoring.
end note
if (strategy == ctr_first?) then (yes)
  :final = 0.2*base + 0.7*ctr + 0.1*fresh;
elseif (strategy == fresh_first?) then (yes)
  :final = 0.2*base + 0.2*ctr + 0.6*fresh;
else (hybrid or other)
  :final = 0.5*base + 0.3*ctr + 0.2*fresh;
endif
:Attach final_score per item\nfrom base_score, ctr_score,\nfreshness_score;
:Sort by final_score;
:Return items, count, strategy;
stop
@enduml
